ive mattersstructured the leasing program for a large shopping center management company with major regional mall holdings throughout the western usacquisition of a multimillion dollar hospital and medical office complex including all related business assetsacquired and disposed of property secured development entitlements drafted restrictive covenants formed homeowners’ associations managed design and construction issues and secured easements in connection with the development of two sizable residential resort communities in puerto ricorepresented a 0person creditors committee in connection with a voluntary  million loan workout program which included securitization work and ongoing management of the disposition of the debtor’s portfolio of 0 multifamily residential propertiessecure and documented a 00 million line of credit for a nationallyrecognized business liquidation and appraisal companyrepresented a major ecommerce company in the formation of an internetbased joint venture with a major entertainment companyprofessional and community activities00 southern california super lawyers super lawyers magazine0 attorney trusted advisor award san fernando valley business journal0 community service award san fernando valley business journalchair valley industry and commerce association vicaboard of directors valley presbyterian hospitalboard of directors new horizonscounsel fit  the causeboard of directors valley economic allianceboard of directors lambda chi alpha international fraternity epsilon sigma chaptervolunteer the alliance for children’s rightsmember american bar associationmember los angeles county bar associationmember san fernando valley bar associationleed – accredited professionaleducationba university of california at los angeles  jd loyola law school admissionsstate of california united states district court central and southern districts of california united states district of puerto rico first and ninth circuit courts of appealspublications  postsjus